        <hr>
        <p>
            Essalamu alaykum wa rahmatu allahi wa barakatuh <br/>
            You recently added the "<strong>{{ mosque.title }}</strong>" mosque located at {{ mosque.localisation }}
            <br/>
            After checking, we find that this mosque already exists on mawaqit
        </p>
        <p>
            Please contact us as soon as possible by whatsapp message at <b>0033612972467</b> (indicate the id
            <b>{{ mosque.id }}</b> of your mosque)
        </p>
